<% title 'Winnamoney | News' %>
<div id="ribbon">
<h1>News</h1>
</div>
<div class="sep">
	<h2>06-01-2009  Winnamoney comes to live</h2>
	<p>Winnamoney starts operations with the Primary Mission of improving the quality of life for all its members. Our Business Philosophy is based on the premise of triumph. We understand the triumph of others as our own success. The welfare of our members is our greatest satisfaction.</p>
</div>

<div class="sep">
	<h2>08-15-2009 Winnamoney opens its first Satellite Office</h2>
