</div>

<div class="sep">
	<h2>09-10-2009 VoIP Telephone Services are included among the products for you to offer!</h2>
	<p>Now you can use and offer the most modern and cutting edge telephone technology services! You will never grow tired of calling worldwide…</p>
</div>

<div class="sep">
	<h2>11-09-2009 Your Personal Website has been completely  remodeled and revamped</h2>
	<p>Incorporating new characteristics  and most functional design, your E-Store is now faster and easier to use. Start enjoying your completely new and updated Web-site.</p>
</div>
<% content_for :rightbar do %>
	<h2>Great Business Opportunity</h2>
	<p>Our Mission at Winnamoney is to contribute to the welfare and quality of life of our Consultants by giving them the tools necessary to develop a profitable business. </p>
	<p>We also strive to have a positive impact on our community by  donating to social projects</p>
	<div class="separator">
		<h2>The Perfect Business Solution</h2>
		<p>Success is within everyone’s reach. To achieve this we must be trained and learn how to develop our business. </p>
		<p>Training Seminars are the perfect solution to the challenges your business is facing today. Stay tuned for the next Training Seminar in your Area!</p>
	</div>
	<h2>Featured product</h2>
	<div class="miniatura">
		<%= image_tag(@product.small_image_url, :width => '90') %>
	</div>
	<p>
		<%= @product.name %>
	<br/>
	<span class="miniprecio"><%= number_to_currency(@product.selling_price) %></span>
	</p>
	<a href="#">
		<% form_tag cart_items_path do  %>
			<%= hidden_field_tag :product_id, @product.id, :class => 'product_id' %>
			<%= image_submit_tag "/images/mini_button.png" %>
		<% end %>
	</a>
<% end %>